      <p>We may share your personal data with your employer in order to validate and administer your account.</p>

      <h2 id="other-caveats">Other caveats</h2>

      <p>If you follow a link from our site to another you are no longer covered by our privacy policy.  We cannot guarantee the security of your data whilst in transmission to our site.</p>

      <p>Any changes we may make to our privacy policy in the future will be posted on this page or sent to you by e-mail.</p>

      <h2 id="contacts">Contacts</h2>

      <p>Questions, comments and requests regarding this privacy policy are welcomed and should be sent to <a href="mailto:datacontroller@theodi.org">datacontroller@theodi.org</a>.</p>

